criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. CAP meets the diagnostic criteria published in 2016 Chinese CAP diagnosis and
             treatment guidelines; CPOPD and AECOPD meet the diagnostic criteria published in
             Chinese 2013 COPD diagnosis and treatment guidelines;

          2. Age ≧ 40years.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. age <40years;

          2. pregnancy;

          3. positive for human immunodeficiency virus (HIV) antibodies;

          4. suspected or confirmed tuberculosis or fungal infection of the lung.
